nodes.text: Hua-Po was a female Lethan Twi'lek and Jedi Master of the Jedi Order. She was stationed on Voss during the Galactic War between the Galactic Republic and the reconstituted Sith Empire.
Hua-Po appears only in the game files for Star Wars: The Old Republic as her character was cut from the game. Hua-Po's file can be found on Jedipedia.
